"},{"pid":"2618ceb01d6a4b651395afb7e19444084fbd4a74","tid":1177711,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1152892bc5f57a5a080e3354cd29d35887706a2","tid":1177711,"uid":191926,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"直接看會覺得呢啲謠言是盲反同無稽之談<br />\n<br />\n但我記得有篇文章<br />\n定有人講過 <br />\n<br />\n滿清玩完前<br />\n<br />\n其中一個問題是呢類民間謠言非常多<br />\n最出名是&quot;快完了&quot;  <br />\n<br />\n信唔信是一回事<br />\n個問題是個社會多人講<br />\n你講 我又講  產生個迴音室效應好大<br />\n<br />\n成個社會充斥呢類國之將亡的異象<br />\n反過來影響很多人的潛意識覺得<br />\n&quot;好像唔惦，要沉船&quot;<br />\n(特別大部份中國人是無咩教育的農民)<br />\n<br />\n中共封哂堆片<br />\n平時唔準唱淡<br />\nyoutube搵堆飛機頻道打飛機<br />\n<br />\n好多時唔係要反對派信<br />\n是為左唔令負面消息<br />\n(就算好無稽)霸哂所有生活空間."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔掛得知youtube d飛機 片低級紅得咁緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc30adbaa621bf053a5bccc8525409dc57a3c34","tid":1177711,"uid":90457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d3c747691a9bed6963c6b970641e5987c30e17ca","tid":1177711,"uid":51920,"like":55,"dislike":218,"score":-163,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"落雨 = 異象<br />\n港毒仔係咪第一日做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"STEAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bce60c88cb5b7cc5e284bde9c01b4a051a1c5c2","tid":1177711,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"屌那星毒霧咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfcf6420f9990469647e65846e477d04fdf5a2b","tid":1177711,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f629f8fe95f72488530cac907d5b81ee54976b4","tid":1177711,"uid":41543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:44:21.00